<p rend="chapter">Tipādabyāsayamakagāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="96"><hi rend="paranum">96</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Tathāgataccheramahosi tassa,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Tathā himāropitadāhasantiṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Tathā hi māro pi tadāha santiṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tathā hi māropi tadā hasantiṃ.</p>
